text: Brian Harman is a professional golfer from Georgia that won the PGA Open Championship in 2023 at the Royal Liverpool. He finished the event with a -13. He went to the University of Georgia. He was born in Savannah, Georgia. He won a prize of $3,000,000 at the 2023 PGA Open Championship.
